CameraServiceGrpc
public static final class CameraServiceGrpc.CameraServiceStub extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractAsyncStub<CameraServiceGrpc.CameraServiceStub>
A stub to allow clients to do asynchronous rpc calls to service CameraService. 
 A CameraService services all cameras associated with a robot
